<name>2GR-FE COOLING</name>
<ttl id="1000C_S000M_72Z7M_T00BA" variety="T00BA">
<name>WATER PUMP</name>
<para id="RM000001IPE001X" category="G" type-id="3001K" name-id="CO0N4-02" from="200601">
<name>INSPECTION</name>
<subpara id="RM000001IPE001X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000001IPE001X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___000064J00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT WATER PUMP ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Visually check the drain hole and air hole for coolant leakage.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A096655E06" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Turn the pulley, and check that the water pump bearing moves smoothly and noiselessly.</ptxt>
<ptxt>If the bearing does not move smoothly and noiselessly, replace the water pump.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
